{"tid":789741,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後正宗讀屎片，連中學生既著期作業都唔識做，你話笑死吾笑死！","createTime":"2018-08-22T12:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T01:18:57.000Z","uid":19334,"like":15,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d0141671cbf80b295dd6e093f24d4b848284bad2","tid":789741,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"話說今日老闆帶左佢仔仔返公司，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫我地有時間就幫下手教佢做著期作業，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仔仔讀聖Joseph，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢就負責打Switch同望住我地做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁D功課都幾深下(D vocab我見都未見過)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢D豬頭骨一定係分比其他人做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就叫隻90後(IVY畢業)幫下手做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就企係係後面望住佢做啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢連袋鼠，長頸鹿，無尾熊呢d咁解單既英文都要Google先識！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n堂堂大學生竟然連份中學生既著期作業都做唔掂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係笑死人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0db29c29efb3bc176e0ae0dc30b1a8cb0db855","tid":789741,"uid":191790,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"3/10 重作"},{"pid":"4cbc8885f3c90ef981d1b40f0b7c5f71436f8102","tid":789741,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"v<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v"},{"pid":"d59241cb747c426e8fcb31376c3e27efb88d9b83","tid":789741,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime