1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"話說今日老闆帶左佢仔仔返公司，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫我地有時間就幫下手教佢做著期作業，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仔仔讀聖Joseph，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢就負責打Switch同望住我地做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁D功課都幾深下(D vocab我見都未見過)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢D豬頭骨一定係分比其他人做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就叫隻90後(IVY畢業)幫下手做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就企係係後面望住佢做啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢連袋鼠，長頸鹿，無尾熊呢d咁解單既英文都要Google先識！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n堂堂大學生竟然連份中學生既著期作業都做唔掂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係笑死人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"我係你老闆，我叫你睇住我個仔做而唔係比佢打機望住你地做，你點做野架撚樣 一陣入黎我間房呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5781af99ff45288e57e880b166b24fc57fd65941","tid":789741,"uid":142026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"人地講 IVE,  你就當人地係IVY"},{"pid":"195f086704e116147490279a0759f1ffe2e73d1a","tid":789741,"uid":71930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"無尾熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a65a6049b2a7b0a709d40d073409f569c036409","tid":789741,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{